{"tid":515990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Now新聞】團體促請政府保障內地新來港人士","createTime":"2018-01-01T02:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T12:03:04.000Z","uid":19213,"like":2,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"32536e5b2f59949d9fa7c7d3da8a786a11bc1670","tid":515990,"uid":19213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:07:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=248781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D248781&d=dBgBEzGz4KVohpnrt7fpUi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b9be7e9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D248781&h=4c37a0da\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=248781</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】社區組織協會調查兒童對政府扶貧表現的滿意度，100分為滿分，只得25分不合格，但已是12年來最高。<br />\n<br />\n多名基層家庭兒童向林鄭月娥的道具表達新一年的期望。<br />\n<br />\n社區組織協會過去一個月訪問二千多名6至17歲的基層家庭兒童，100分滿分，他們認為政府過去一年的扶貧表現只得25分，是調查2005年以來最高。<br />\n<br />\n最滿意的是房屋政策，團體認同政府推出社會房屋共享計劃改善居住環境，但仍有不少兒童住所不理想。<br />\n<br />\n其次滿意的是教育政策，認為幼稚園免費教育雖紓緩基層壓力，但其他資助仍然不足。<br />\n<br />\n受訪兒童關注被歧視問題，認為政府未有改善。13歲的黃愛玲來港4年，有親身經歷。<br />\n<br />\n團體促請政府修訂種族歧視條例，保障內地新來港人士。"},{"pid":"d292220b74c8222dffd0709ac877647cb8172dd2","tid":515990,"uid":23170,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:18:47.000Z","msg":"死左膠，又攞人地啲錢同福利去做好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84848ed403807fde61fb992308806396c25fde29","tid":515990,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:20:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a755c78696716801ee017e2a7e6bf5a36816b4c","tid":515990,"uid":62815,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:29:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p